(349, 'document', 'text/html', 'Kindergartens and schools', '', '', 'schools-and-kindergartens', '', 1, 0, 0, 342, 1, '', '<p>Preschool and school educational institutions are objects, that need high-quality, reliable, and, what is the most important, safe products for cleaning and disinfection of furniture and toys, all surfaces, including kitchens and bathrooms. Physical health of children is determined by many factors, including quality of cleaning activities in various divisions of one or another of the children''s institutions. Professional cleaning means cope even the most persistent and unusual types of pollution, while possessing a number of advantages, the most important of which is safety for people, surfaces and environment.</p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<ul class=list3>\r\n<p>Disinfection of surfaces</p>\r\n<li>Disinfection of medical devices</li>\r\n<li>Disinfection of medical waste</li>\r\n<li>Hygiene of skin</li>\r\n<li>Disinfection in public catering places</li>\r\n<li>Housekeeping</li>\r\n<li>Floor treatment</li>\r\n<li>Cleaning of sanitary rooms and swimming pools</li>\r\n<li>Kitchens cleaning</li>\r\n<li>Dishwashing</li>\r\n<li>Washing of thermal equipment</li>\r\n<li>Treatment of floors and surfaces</li>\r\n<li>Washing of glass surfaces</li>\r\n<li>Treatment of metal surfaces</li>\r\n<li>Removal of stains and graffiti</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p> </p>', 1, 8, 6, 1, 1, 1, 1386590682, 94, 1488629882, 0, 0, 0, 1386590640, 1, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'modDocument', 'en', 1, 'catalog/schools-and-kindergartens.html', 0, 0, 1, NULL),
